# Testing Rules

- Every new feature must include automated tests; every bug fix must include a failing test first (regression)
- Prefer unit tests for business logic; integration tests for APIs and flows
- Use project stack: pytest (Python), React Testing Library / Jest (frontend), etc.
- Test edge cases and error conditions; keep tests readable and maintainable
- If something cannot be tested, justify in PR with mitigation plan
- Run test suite before PR and in CI; no merge with failing tests
